Sadie Corré https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sadie_Corr%C3%A9 0 Sadie Corré (31 May 1918 – 26 August 2009) was an English actress, tap dancer, comic performer and leading pantomime cat. She was sometimes credited as Sadie Corrie. Sadie_Corré ( 31_May_1918 – 26_August_2009 ) was an_English_actress , tap_dancer , comic_performer and leading pantomime_cat .
